dc_title_s: Plat book of Genesee County, Michigan
dc_description_s: Extent: 1 atlas (18 unnumbered pages) | Abstract: Atlas of township property maps showing names of rural landowners. | Notes: Publication date estimated by absence of Michigan highway numbers, in comparison with later Hixson plat book of Genesee County that shows Michigan highway numbers.|Scale determined from section lines. | Scale approximately 1:51,000
